source:
TEXT_DUNGEONCRYSTALTOWER3_00000_CLOUDOFDARKNESS_000_000Who disturbs the gloom?
Ahhh, mortals from the realm of light.
You have not stumbled here without purpose...
target:
TEXT_DUNGEONCRYSTALTOWER3_00000_CLOUDOFDARKNESS_000_000知らず迷いこんだわけではあるまいな……
小さき者…… あわき光よ……

source:
TEXT_DUNGEONCRYSTALTOWER3_00000_CLOUDOFDARKNESS_000_010I am the Cloud of Darkness.
What I do not smother, I devour.
What I cannot devour, I destroy.
target:
TEXT_DUNGEONCRYSTALTOWER3_00000_CLOUDOFDARKNESS_000_010私は 暗闇の雲……
すべてを覆い 喰らい 蹂躙する

source:
TEXT_DUNGEONCRYSTALTOWER3_00000_CLOUDOFDARKNESS_000_020The covenant is everlasting.
All mortals before the flood of darkness
will sink lifeless into the void!
target: TEXT_DUNGEONCRYSTALTOWER3_00000_CLOUDOFDARKNESS_000_020<tab>契約を果たし お前たちの光の世界をも 無に還すのだ！
